'''轴丘'''（{{lang|en|Axon hillock}}）是指[[神经元|神经元]]中[[细胞体|细胞体]]靠近[[轴突|轴突]]的区域、紧邻轴突初始段（{{lang|en|initial segment}}）<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1083/jcb.38.1.193|pmid=5691973|pmc=2107452|title=The Axon Hillock and the Initial Segment|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-cell-biology_1968-07_38_1/page/193|journal=The Journal of Cell Biology|volume=38|issue=1|pages=193–201|year=1968|last1=Palay|first1=Sanford L.|last2=Sotelo|first2=Constantino|last3=Peters|first3=Alan|last4=Orkand|first4=Paula M.}}</ref><ref name="MihailoffHaines2018">{{cite journal|last1=Mihailoff|first1=G.A.|last2=Haines|first2=D.E.|title=The Cell Biology of Neurons and Glia|year=2018|pages=15–33.e1|doi=10.1016/B978-0-323-39632-5.00002-5}}</ref>。轴丘区域含有较多的[[電壓門控離子通道|电压门控]][[钠离子通道|钠离子通道]]<ref name="KotermanskiCascio2016">{{cite journal|last1=Kotermanski|first1=S.E.|last2=Cascio|first2=M.|title=Neuronal Action Potentials and Ion Channel Allostery|year=2016|pages=244–251|doi=10.1016/B978-0-12-394447-4.10028-8}}</ref>，该区域也含有一定量的[[尼氏体|尼氏体]]（[[粗面内质网|粗面内质网]]）<ref name="BradyTai2012">{{cite journal|last1=Brady|first1=Scott T.|last2=Tai|first2=Leon|title=Cell Biology of the Nervous System|year=2012|pages=3–25|doi=10.1016/B978-0-12-374947-5.00001-8}}</ref>。

